      <image source="Visual_Onebit_50_positive.png" width="10%" />
      <image source="L3-4-twoqubitvisual.png" width="10%" />
      <p> </p>
    </sidebyside>
    -->

    <p> 
      In the images above, the left side is a single qubit in 
      50/50 superposition. The right side is two different qubits, one  
      <m>\ket{0}</m> and the other <m>\ket{1}</m>.
    </p>

  </section>

